      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlapalli tlen ce ixcopincayotl tlen cencah itlachiyaliz zan iyo tliltic, nextic, ihuan iztac, nochipa neci tenextic; quen mopahpa ce tlamantli, motequihuia iixpan vidrioh tlen mopahpahtoc, ipan esmaltes, ipan chachapalli huan cequinoc tlamantli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
